rance.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 745, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.9999583190877879, \"rank\": 4.146488040123984e-05, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 763, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9998923232421773, \"rank\": 9.598152273179299e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"Souheil\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 619}, {\"ngram\": \"El Khalfaoui's 19-year-old son\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"a police officer\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 686}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"a traffic stop\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 732}, {\"ngram\": \"the south\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The investigation was closed for the first time in December 2021, then relaunched by a new complaint and entrusted to another jurisdiction.\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The investigation\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 830}, {\"ngram\": \"a new complaint\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"another jurisdiction\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the investigations have not progressed for three years.\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the investigations\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 974}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The police offi