50, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mediapart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mediapart\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mediapart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mediapart\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his sister's appeal\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1271}, {\"ngram\": \"Issam El Khalfaoui\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"his outrage\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"the digital news outlet\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The spokesperson for the Paris 2024 Olympic Games organizing committee, Anne Descamps, said on Tuesday that the opening ceremony artists were hired by an external production agency and that \\\"the selection was based on their creative skills.\\\"\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1448, \"end\": 1456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The spokesperson\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"committee\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony artists\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"an external production agency\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"the selection\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"their creative skills\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"IGPN investigation documents indicate that Souheil El Khalfaoui endangered the life of another officer by backing up during a traffic stop.\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrase